parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fracture of the dashboard can cause airbag deployment issues, leading to injuries or fatalities.

symptoms: The dashboard starts to lift from the driver's side window to the end of the steering wheel
the dashboard is buckling up in front of the driver
the dashboard is separating from the windshield cowl
the dashboard is warping and pulling away from the vent area.
